'''Dashiell "Dash" Garcia''' (2255 - 2310) was an American professional baseball player. He was the son football player [[Jeremy Garcia]], grandson actor [[Jorge Garcia]], great-grandson of actress [[Desiree Garcia]], great-great-grandson of art gallery professional [[Lynn Garcia]], great-great-great-grandson of magician [[Odell Garcia]], great-great-great-great-grandson of businessman [[Eduardo Garcia]], great-great-great-great-great-grandson of baseball player [[Colt Garcia]], and great-great-great-great-great-great-grandson of musician [[Donald Garcia]]. 

